<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>自性 - 标签 - 无名老人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%87%AA%E6%80%A7/</link><description>无名老人的文章</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 21:15:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%87%AA%E6%80%A7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>迷心外见不见性</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%BF%B7%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%81%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 21:15:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%BF%B7%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%81%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="迷心外见不见性"&gt;&lt;span&gt;迷心外见不见性&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%bf%b7%e5%bf%83%e5%a4%96%e8%a7%81%e4%b8%8d%e8%a7%81%e6%80%a7" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：偈子、见性、自性、小根、外修、法布施、无取无舍、佛子、修行、觉悟&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　迷心外见，修行觅佛，淫欲难了，说明未悟自性，即是小根之人。若经开示顿悟佛知见，不执外修，於自心常起正见，外尘不染，即是见性。此理虽明，奈何世人多执文字表相，不知心正法正、本心即性。今以偈直指，愿诸佛子返照自心，莫向外求。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>偈子：低级趣味心中著</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%8E%E7%BA%A7%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E8%91%97/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 20:15:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%8E%E7%BA%A7%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E8%91%97/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="低级趣味心中著"&gt;&lt;span&gt;低级趣味心中著&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%8e%e7%ba%a7%e8%b6%a3%e5%91%b3%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%ad%e8%91%97" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：偈子、低级趣味、业力、我执、不二法门、无取无舍、佛子、修行、觉悟、自性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　众生沉沦，多因心中执著低级趣味，被业力牵扰，身不由己，苦中堕落。此偈直指凡夫在对错、善恶、有为之间反复徘徊，皆因我执攀缘，难入中道觉路。唯有悟入不二法门，超越对错善恶，方能坐法空座，得无所挂碍。今录此偈，愿诸佛子破执离缚，归向无取无舍之真实。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>偈子：孤芳自赏纸上功</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%AD%A4%E8%8A%B3%E8%87%AA%E8%B5%8F%E7%BA%B8%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%9F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%AD%A4%E8%8A%B3%E8%87%AA%E8%B5%8F%E7%BA%B8%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%9F/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="孤芳自赏纸上功"&gt;&lt;span&gt;孤芳自赏纸上功&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ad%a4%e8%8a%b3%e8%87%aa%e8%b5%8f%e7%ba%b8%e4%b8%8a%e5%8a%9f" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：偈子、无取无舍、五蕴、实相、不二法门、佛子、修行、觉悟、自性、见性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　学佛修行，贵在明心见性，不在文字功名。此偈直指时人通病：或孤芳自赏于纸上功夫，或沉溺名利于学术研究，或饰句雕文而增益自我，却不知五蕴本空，不二法门方为真道。今录此偈，愿诸佛子返照自心，莫向外求。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>偈子：放逸与涅槃</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%94%BE%E9%80%B8%E4%B8%8E%E6%B6%85%E6%A7%83/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:45:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%94%BE%E9%80%B8%E4%B8%8E%E6%B6%85%E6%A7%83/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="放逸与涅槃"&gt;&lt;span&gt;放逸与涅槃&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%94%be%e9%80%b8%e4%b8%8e%e6%b6%85%e6%a7%83" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、放逸、有为法、涅槃、甘露、常乐我净、修行、佛法、觉悟、自性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　《大般涅槃经》中，佛陀以简洁而深刻的对仗，揭示了放逸与涅槃、苦与乐的根本分界。经文指出：放逸者沉溺于有为法，招致第一之苦；不放逸者趣向涅槃，得究竟之乐。此段经文虽短，却是修行人辨别正邪、抉择取舍的明灯。今录于此，愿诸佛子深体佛意，舍放逸而趣涅槃。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>偈子：心平何劳持戒</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%BF%83%E5%B9%B3%E4%BD%95%E5%8A%B3%E6%8C%81%E6%88%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%BF%83%E5%B9%B3%E4%BD%95%E5%8A%B3%E6%8C%81%E6%88%92/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="心平何劳持戒"&gt;&lt;span&gt;心平何劳持戒&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%bf%83%e5%b9%b3%e4%bd%95%e5%8a%b3%e6%8c%81%e6%88%92" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：慧能大师、六祖、无相颂、修行、持戒、菩提、自性、般若、佛法、觉悟&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　此偈乃六祖慧能大师所作《无相颂》，载于《六祖坛经》。其文直指心性，破除外相执著，阐明修行根本在于自心觉悟，而非外在形式。所谓“心平何劳持戒，行直何用修禅”，即是明心见性之后，戒定慧自然具足，不假外求。今录此偈，愿诸佛子依此修行，返照自心，当下即是净土。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>大乘义</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%90%E5%BA%94%E6%82%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%90%E5%BA%94%E6%82%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="佛子应悟大乘义方离自误愚"&gt;&lt;span&gt;佛子应悟大乘义，方离自误愚&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%9b%e5%ad%90%e5%ba%94%e6%82%9f%e5%a4%a7%e4%b9%98%e4%b9%89%e6%96%b9%e7%a6%bb%e8%87%aa%e8%af%af%e6%84%9a" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、无所得、菩萨、大乘、六祖、自性、净戒、佛性、心行、觉悟&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;本文汇集《大般涅槃经》《宝积经》《法华经》《四十二章经》及六祖慧能大师开示，阐明菩萨净戒、无所得义、自性自度之真谛，以警末世学佛人依佛知见，离颠倒执，入正定聚。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>大乘义</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/bodhisattva-meaning/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2017 23:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/bodhisattva-meaning/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="佛子应悟大乘义方离自误愚"&gt;&lt;span&gt;佛子应悟大乘义，方离自误愚&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%9b%e5%ad%90%e5%ba%94%e6%82%9f%e5%a4%a7%e4%b9%98%e4%b9%89%e6%96%b9%e7%a6%bb%e8%87%aa%e8%af%af%e6%84%9a" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、大乘、无所得、自性、菩萨、善爱、净戒、六祖、法华经、如来&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;末世学佛，多迷四大为身，妄想为心，心外求法，愈求愈苦。佛于《大般涅槃经》中分明开示善爱、不善爱之别，菩萨无所得之真实义，以及清净持戒之五法佐助。又引《宝积经》、《法华经》及六祖法语，直指自性自度、心行佛道。今依经教，一字不易，略加分节，以助佛子悟入大乘，远离自误。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>信仰</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%8B%A5%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E4%BA%86%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%89%E6%82%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0-%E6%AD%A3%E7%9C%9F%E4%B9%8B%E9%81%93%E5%BF%85%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4%E7%9B%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%94/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2017 15:29:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%8B%A5%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E4%BA%86%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%89%E6%82%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0-%E6%AD%A3%E7%9C%9F%E4%B9%8B%E9%81%93%E5%BF%85%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4%E7%9B%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%94/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="若离开了对觉悟二字的信仰正真之道必成群盲的迷途"&gt;&lt;span&gt;若离开了对“觉悟”二字的信仰，正真之道必成群盲的迷途&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%8b%a5%e7%a6%bb%e5%bc%80%e4%ba%86%e5%af%b9%e8%a7%89%e6%82%9f%e4%ba%8c%e5%ad%97%e7%9a%84%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%b0%e6%ad%a3%e7%9c%9f%e4%b9%8b%e9%81%93%e5%bf%85%e6%88%90%e7%be%a4%e7%9b%b2%e7%9a%84%e8%bf%b7%e9%80%94" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：若离开了对、觉悟、二字的信仰、正真之道必成群盲的迷途、佛法、智慧、真理、自性、人民、涅槃&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;　　2017-01-17 佛弟子 觉悟与和谐&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人以为只要有知识、有热情、有行动，就一定能走在正路上，却忽略了一个决定方向的根本问题：如果对“觉悟”本身没有信心，那么再多努力也可能只是在黑暗中彼此牵引。本文正是针对这种以为“可以不谈觉悟、只谈做事”的误解，指出离开觉悟二字之后，所谓正道何以会变成群盲并行的迷途。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>清净一心</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/2017%E5%8F%A4%E5%8E%866%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E5%96%84%E6%99%BA%E5%B8%88%E5%BC%80%E7%A4%BA/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2017 14:08:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/2017%E5%8F%A4%E5%8E%866%E6%9C%8819%E6%97%A5%E5%96%84%E6%99%BA%E5%B8%88%E5%BC%80%E7%A4%BA/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="2017古历6月19日善智师开示"&gt;&lt;span&gt;2017古历6月19日善智师开示&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#2017%e5%8f%a4%e5%8e%866%e6%9c%8819%e6%97%a5%e5%96%84%e6%99%ba%e5%b8%88%e5%bc%80%e7%a4%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：觉悟、修行、智慧、自性、大乘、涅槃、平等、学佛、佛法、真理&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人学佛时，一听到“观”“忏悔”“大乘”“普贤行”这些词，就容易把它们理解成外在形式，或者只停留在文字领会之上，以为多听、多记、多谈就是修行的进步。可若不先弄清什么是正观，什么是邪观，什么是向内照见，什么是仍在妄心里打转，那么表面上在学佛，实际却可能离正道越来越远。本文这篇开示，核心就在于引人回到“识本心、见本性、明因果、入正观”这一条真正的修学路径。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>献给建军90周年</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%9B%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%91%E7%8C%AE%E7%BB%99%E5%BB%BA%E5%86%9B90%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8F%82%E5%A4%A9%E5%8F%A4%E6%A0%91-%E6%9E%9D%E7%B9%81%E5%8F%B6%E8%8C%82-%E5%B0%B1%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E6%A0%B9%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%94%E6%B7%B1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2017 14:05:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%9B%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%91%E7%8C%AE%E7%BB%99%E5%BB%BA%E5%86%9B90%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8F%82%E5%A4%A9%E5%8F%A4%E6%A0%91-%E6%9E%9D%E7%B9%81%E5%8F%B6%E8%8C%82-%E5%B0%B1%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E6%A0%B9%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%94%E6%B7%B1/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="原创首发献给建军90周年参天古树枝繁叶茂就源於根正且深"&gt;&lt;span&gt;（原创首发）献给建军90周年——参天古树、枝繁叶茂，就源於根正且深&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%8e%9f%e5%88%9b%e9%a6%96%e5%8f%91%e7%8c%ae%e7%bb%99%e5%bb%ba%e5%86%9b90%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4%e5%8f%82%e5%a4%a9%e5%8f%a4%e6%a0%91%e6%9e%9d%e7%b9%81%e5%8f%b6%e8%8c%82%e5%b0%b1%e6%ba%90%e6%96%bc%e6%a0%b9%e6%ad%a3%e4%b8%94%e6%b7%b1" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：原创首发、献给建军90周年、参天古树、枝繁叶茂、就源於根正且深、佛法、觉悟、智慧、真理、自性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　一谈强军，很多人先想到的是武器、编制、训练和外在纪律，以为只要靠制度约束和装备升级，军队自然就会强起来；但这类看法往往忽略了一个更根本的问题：如果人的心被私欲、错认和颠倒牵着走，再强的外力也可能反过来伤己害人。本文要讨论的，正是“强军”与“军强”的差别，并把问题引向一个更深的层面：决定胜负与兴衰的，究竟是外在打造，还是内在觉悟？&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>见性之人？</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/seeing-nature-with-sections/</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 Apr 2017 22:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/seeing-nature-with-sections/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="何为真正的见性之人"&gt;&lt;span&gt;何为真正的见性之人？&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%95%e4%b8%ba%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e7%9a%84%e8%a7%81%e6%80%a7%e4%b9%8b%e4%ba%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：见性、功德、六祖大师、平等、念念无滞、自性、达摩、法华经、实相、佛性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;见性成佛，是禅宗乃至整个大乘佛法的核心。然而何为真正的见性？它与福德、功德有何区别？见性之人日常心行又有何特征？本文依六祖大师对见性与功德的精要开示，结合《法华经》、达摩祖师语录，层层剖析真正见性之人的内在境界与外显德相。原文一字不易，仅于各段前加小标题，并首尾略作导引与总结，以助读者契入实相。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>偈子：迷人求法不求心</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%81%88%E5%AD%903/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 Jun 2014 15:18:22 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%81%88%E5%AD%903/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="迷人求法不求心"&gt;&lt;span&gt;迷人求法不求心&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%bf%b7%e4%ba%ba%e6%b1%82%e6%b3%95%e4%b8%8d%e6%b1%82%e5%bf%83" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：修行、佛法、觉悟、智慧、真理、自性、见性、人民、大乘&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　不少人对偈子的理解停留在“像诗一样”，以为读懂字面就算明白了意义；但真正重要的，往往是它借短句压缩出来的判断与提醒。本文所列偈子，正是在极简文字中指出修行与迷执之间的关键分野，帮助读者从熟视无睹处重新回头。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>得佛心印，人人皆弥勒</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%9B%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%86%E5%BC%A5%E5%8B%92/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 May 2014 18:11:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%9B%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%86%E5%BC%A5%E5%8B%92/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="得佛心印人人皆弥勒"&gt;&lt;span&gt;得佛心印，人人皆弥勒&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%be%97%e4%bd%9b%e5%bf%83%e5%8d%b0%e4%ba%ba%e4%ba%ba%e7%9a%86%e5%bc%a5%e5%8b%92" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：得佛心印、人人皆弥勒、佛法、觉悟、修行、智慧、自性、见性、大乘、涅槃&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一听“弥勒降世”或“得佛心印”，就容易往神异、传奇、少数人的特殊身份上去想，结果反而把佛法里最重要的一层遮住了：佛所说的觉悟、见性、正知见，究竟是不是人人本具、人人可行？若把“弥勒”只当作外在等待的对象，而不从自心去求佛性、从正法去辨真假，那么再多预言、诗句和传说，也只是热闹而已。本文正是借一段流传的诗证，引回到佛法本义，说明何谓真佛弟子，何谓心出家，以及为何说若真依佛义，人人皆可成弥勒。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>从一个信字去体悟难报的佛恩</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BF%A1%E5%AD%97%E5%8E%BB%E4%BD%93%E6%82%9F%E9%9A%BE%E6%8A%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9B%E6%81%A9/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 May 2014 12:54:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BF%A1%E5%AD%97%E5%8E%BB%E4%BD%93%E6%82%9F%E9%9A%BE%E6%8A%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9B%E6%81%A9/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="从一个信字去体悟难报的佛恩"&gt;&lt;span&gt;从一个信字去体悟难报的佛恩&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bb%8e%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e4%bf%a1%e5%ad%97%e5%8e%bb%e4%bd%93%e6%82%9f%e9%9a%be%e6%8a%a5%e7%9a%84%e4%bd%9b%e6%81%a9" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：佛法、觉悟、修行、智慧、真理、自性、见性、人民、大乘、涅槃&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一说“信佛”，往往想到的是口头承认、情感依赖，或者在遇到难处时求一点安慰和保佑；可这样的“信”，既经不起境界，也带不出真实修行。真正的“信”，不是糊里糊涂地跟随，更不是把佛法当成方便求福的工具，而是对真理、因果、正法与解脱之路的真实认领。本文正是从一个“信”字出发，去说明何谓正信、为何要信、以及为何越体会这份正信，就越能感到佛恩深重难报。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>何为真正的见性之人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 May 2014 12:44:16 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="何为真正的见性之人"&gt;&lt;span&gt;何为真正的见性之人&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%95%e4%b8%ba%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e7%9a%84%e8%a7%81%e6%80%a7%e4%b9%8b%e4%ba%ba" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：何为真正的见性之人、智慧、自性、见性、平等、佛法、觉悟、修行、真理、人民&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一听“见性”，要么把它神秘化，以为那是极少数人才有的玄妙体验；要么又把它简单化，觉得自己懂几句道理、会说几句空义，就已经算是“见性”。但真正的问题在于：若心行没有变，烦恼没有减，执着没有松，所谓见性到底凭什么成立？本文正是围绕这一误区，追问何为真正的见性之人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>二障不除，空说大乘！</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BA%8C%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E9%99%A4-%E7%A9%BA%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2014 10:49:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BA%8C%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E9%99%A4-%E7%A9%BA%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="二障不除空说大乘"&gt;&lt;span&gt;二障不除，空说大乘！&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%ba%8c%e9%9a%9c%e4%b8%8d%e9%99%a4%e7%a9%ba%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a7%e4%b9%98" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：二障不除、空说大乘、佛法、觉悟、修行、智慧、真理、自性、见性、大乘&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一谈大乘，就喜欢谈慈悲、谈菩萨道、谈利益众生，甚至把高妙言辞当成了修行深入的证明。可若回到自心去看，烦恼障与所知障是否真实减薄了，贪欲无明是否仍旧牵引着自己，那便会发现，大乘之“说”与大乘之“行”往往并不是一回事。本文正是要指出：若二障不除，只在名相上夸谈大乘，不但无益于解脱，反而更容易落入自欺与空谈。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>修行人的初觉</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E8%A7%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2014 15:35:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E8%A7%89/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="修行人的初觉"&gt;&lt;span&gt;修行人的初觉&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bf%ae%e8%a1%8c%e4%ba%ba%e7%9a%84%e5%88%9d%e8%a7%89" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：修行人的初觉、修行、智慧、真理、自性、见性、大乘、涅槃、平等、学佛&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　很多人一谈修行，先想到的是做多少功课、读多少经典、积多少形式上的“功德”，却很少追问：自己到底为什么会苦？所修之法究竟是在离苦，还是仍在妄心中追逐外相？若这个根本问题不先照见，所谓修行就很容易落入求福、求相、求感应、求回报的旧路上。本文所说的“初觉”，正是要把人从这种外求误区中拉回来，使其真正看见凡夫之苦从何而起，正因又当如何立起。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>